### FindAll
POST http://localhost/graphql
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "query": "query FindAll { findAll { id username first last email } }"
}

### FindById
POST http://localhost/graphql
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "query": "query FindById($id: ID!) { findById(id: $id) { id username first last email password department { id name } roles { id name } } }",
  "variables": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

